INSERT INTO quotes (id, content, author_id, views) VALUES (457851, 'At the end of the day, my goal was to be the best hacker.', 49891, 0), (457852, 'I think we all have blocks between us and the best version of ourselves, whether it''s shyness, insecurity, anxiety, whether it''s a physical block, and the story of a person overcoming that block to their best self. It''s truly inspiring because I think all of us are engaged in that every day.', 72936, 0), (457853, 'My best vacation is somewhere I could hide, somewhere warm and not a lot of people around.', 66702, 0), (457854, 'The best way to guarantee a loss is to quit.', 30247, 0), (457855, 'You have to be confident in who you are and what you''re doing. Of course, you try to evolve. I would never tell you, ''Today is the best I will ever be.'' I''m always trying to be a better chef, a better dad, a better person.', 69247, 0), (457856, 'Falling in love is the best way to kill your heart because then it''s not yours anymore. It''s laid in a coffin, waiting to be cremated.', 69262, 0), (457857, 'I think one great tip is that you should always love yourself. If you don''t love yourself, take care of yourself, cater to yourself and that little inner voice, you will really not be very worthy of being with someone else, because you won''t be the best version of you.', 69226, 0), (457858, 'Being fully present is the best guarantee for a bright future.', 10151, 0), (457859, 'If you''re thinking of coming to America, this is what it''s like: you''ve got your Comfort Inn, you''ve got your Best Western, and you''ve got your Red Lobster where you eat. Everybody''s very fat, everybody''s very stupid and everybody''s very rude - it''s not a holiday programme, it''s the truth.', 12899, 0), (457860, 'The best doctor is the one you run to and can''t find.', 2879, 0), (457861, 'Try and leave this world a little better than you found it, and when your turn comes to die, you can die happy in feeling that at any rate, you have not wasted your time but have done your best.', 36714, 0), (457862, 'I never had a policy I have just tried to do my very best each and every day.', 1012, 0), (457863, 'You have to accept whatever comes and the only important thing is that you meet it with courage and with the best that you have to give.', 141, 0), (457864, 'Every kid has a toy that they believe is their best friend, that they believe communicates with them, and they imagine it being alive, their toy horse or car or whatever it is. Stop-motion is the only medium where we literally can make a toy come to life, an actual object.', 68294, 0), (457865, 'Trust is not simply a matter of truthfulness, or even constancy. It is also a matter of amity and goodwill. We trust those who have our best interests at heart, and mistrust those who seem deaf to our concerns.', 30035, 0), (457866, 'We have the best government that money can buy.', 286, 0), (457867, 'Living with fear stops us taking risks, and if you don''t go out on the branch, you''re never going to get the best fruit.', 67259, 0), (457868, 'Surround yourself with the best people you can find, delegate authority, and don''t interfere as long as the policy you''ve decided upon is being carried out.', 1727, 0), (457869, 'Compassion may be defined as the capacity to be attentive to the experience of others, to wish the best for others, and to sense what will truly serve others.', 39477, 0), (457870, 'Design is a plan for arranging elements in such a way as best to accomplish a particular purpose.', 3631, 0), (457871, 'It is with children that we have the best chance of studying the development of logical knowledge, mathematical knowledge, physical knowledge, and so forth.', 9651, 0), (457872, 'Most businesses think that product is the most important thing, but without great leadership, mission and a team that deliver results at a high level, even the best product won''t make a company successful.', 66592, 0), (457873, 'If you want to be the best, you have to do things that other people aren''t willing to do.', 30837, 0), (457874, 'No man really knows about other human beings. The best he can do is to suppose that they are like himself.', 1070, 0), (457875, 'Right actions in the future are the best apologies for bad actions in the past.', 9316, 0), (457876, 'Success comes from knowing that you did your best to become the best that you are capable of becoming.', 1721, 0), (457877, 'In my own relationships, I know that I should break up with someone who doesn''t encourage me to be strong and make my own choices and do what''s best in my life, so if you''re dating someone who doesn''t want you to be the best person you can be, you shouldn''t be dating them.', 73, 0), (457878, 'Living well is the best revenge.', 3428, 0), (457879, 'The best place to find God is in a garden. You can dig for him there.', 266, 0), (457880, 'The best part of being a mom to me is the unconditional love. I have never felt a love as pure, a love that''s as rewarding.', 72635, 0), (457881, 'Every job is good if you do your best and work hard. A man who works hard stinks only to the ones that have nothing to do but smell.', 17296, 0), (457882, 'A person who has been punished is not less inclined to behave in a given way; at best, he learns how to avoid punishment.', 627, 0), (457883, 'Yes''m, old friends is always best, ''less you can catch a new one that''s fit to make an old one out of.', 844, 0), (457884, 'Choose your corner, pick away at it carefully, intensely and to the best of your ability and that way you might change the world.', 3631, 0), (457885, 'The patient''s autonomy always, always should be respected, even if it is absolutely contrary - the decision is contrary to best medical advice and what the physician wants.', 7905, 0), (457886, 'I would say I''m a nice person, and I take pride in the fact that I treat everyone really well, so there''s no reason for anyone to ever come at me because I only want the best for everybody else.', 682, 0),